@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@tenantId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@accessToken = {{token}}

### Get Assets (Paged)
GET {{baseUrl}}/assets?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### Create Asset
POST {{baseUrl}}/assets
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "name": "资产-001"
}
